(176683, 'BE00ED76-2E2C-4F67-B491-B15A31EA29D8', 'Dear Nitzan, a little something to wake up to. I love how you are thoughtful and caring and sweet to the core. It is absolutely infectious. I know I wrote that I want to be a force for good, but you are, tirelessly. I feel I have much to learn from you. I feel challenged by you...intellectually and emotionally (and physically...tough work out!) and I think I can offer you the same. Your feedback and insights into how I''m processing my situation  demonstrate how you can truly put yourself in some else''s shoes...whether mine or marla''s, and you are  non-judgmental and patient. I''m a bit afraid to just dive in with you...for the reasons we discussed. But I think of being with you a few nights ago,  so  close to you, looking into your eyes.  I felt loved, a deep joy and trust. I hope you felt the same way. Wish i could wake up next to you, help you finish your memo and kiss that beautiful face all over. Goodnight. I hope you are having peaceful, sweet dreams.  ', 'David', 'Nitzan', '2015-07-26T23:15:51'),
